article_title: Officer Killed In Afghanistan Taken To NY
article_text: The body of one of the six U.S. troops killed in a suicide attack in Afghanistan last week was returned to New York Monday. Members of the New York Air National Guard, the NYPD and Joseph Lemm's family were at Stewart Air National Guard Base. (Dec. AP
